  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1411770/extras/b5e3938763592063ee0eed7e7fdedae5.webp?t=1772682754\" width=616 height=60 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A fast-paced run and gun where procedural enemy waves unleash a demonic invasion from the Underworld.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Redd, an orphan raised by a master sorceress, was trained in magic to protect humanity from supernatural horrors. But when an unknown attacker executed her mother, everything changed. Scarred and emotionally shattered, she turned away from her teammates.<br><br>Now, Brock City is collapsing under a supernatural assault.<br><br>Dash through relentless enemy waves, unleash devastating spells, and fight alongside the Legion of Sorcerers against swarms of dark creatures. Unlock new abilities and confront the vengeance rising within her.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1411770/extras/1c12e171d9105a0cf2c9857b09200df8.avif?t=1772682754\" width=616 height=346 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1411770/extras/5b63d543a27d91cf91f02a7284d65bd9.webp?t=1772682754\" width=616 height=60 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fast-paced 2D run-and-gun combat with dynamic procedural enemy waves.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master powerful spells and switch between them instantly to adapt on the fly.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight through 6 nightmarish worlds, each culminating in a giant boss encounter.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A dark fusion of Halloween atmosphere and Day of the Dead mythos.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Test your skill in Arcade, Endless, and Boss Rush modes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join Redd's fight for revenge as the Underworld overruns Brock City.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1411770/extras/65c896eeb6fa87e3fb49aa8bb61a660b.avif?t=1772682754\" width=616 height=200 /></span> </p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1411770/extras/b5e3938763592063ee0eed7e7fdedae5.webp?t=1772682754\" width=616 height=60 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A fast-paced run and gun where procedural enemy waves unleash a demonic invasion from the Underworld.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Redd, an orphan raised by a master sorceress, was trained in magic to protect humanity from supernatural horrors. But when an unknown attacker executed her mother, everything changed. Scarred and emotionally shattered, she turned away from her teammates.<br><br>Now, Brock City is collapsing under a supernatural assault.<br><br>Dash through relentless enemy waves, unleash devastating spells, and fight alongside the Legion of Sorcerers against swarms of dark creatures. Unlock new abilities and confront the vengeance rising within her.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1411770/extras/1c12e171d9105a0cf2c9857b09200df8.avif?t=1772682754\" width=616 height=346 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1411770/extras/5b63d543a27d91cf91f02a7284d65bd9.webp?t=1772682754\" width=616 height=60 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fast-paced 2D run-and-gun combat with dynamic procedural enemy waves.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master powerful spells and switch between them instantly to adapt on the fly.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight through 6 nightmarish worlds, each culminating in a giant boss encounter.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A dark fusion of Halloween atmosphere and Day of the Dead mythos.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Test your skill in Arcade, Endless, and Boss Rush modes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join Redd's fight for revenge as the Underworld overruns Brock City.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1411770/extras/65c896eeb6fa87e3fb49aa8bb61a660b.avif?t=1772682754\" width=616 height=200 /></span> </p>",
